  <name>CoBang</name>
  <summary>QR code scanner for Linux desktop</summary>
  <description>
    <p>A missing native QR Code scanner application for Linux desktop.</p>
    <p>CoBang can scan from webcam or from static image.
 It is written in Python, using GTK+ for UI, GStreamer for webcam capture
 and a part of ZBar for decoding QR code from image.</p>
  </description>
